     FANBPW58 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FMBDPL02 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAAFTL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAAHTL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFCEPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFGBPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FABRWP58 IF  E           K        DISK                      A
     FQPRINT  O   F     132     OF     PRINTER                        UC
      *-----------------------------------------------------
     E                    TTX     1   1 70
     E                    TOT     1   2 11
     E                    CMD     1   1 75
     E                    ARX        75  1
     E                    ERR     1   5 70
     E                    MON    12  12  3
     E                    W#M         6  3
      *-----------------------------------------------------
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140W@TIME
     I                                        1   60@@TIME
     I                                        1   20W@TH
     I                                        3   40W@TM
     I                                        5   60W@TS
     I                                        7  100W@DY
     I                                       11  120W@DM
     I                                       13  140W@DD
